In [28]:
mse = []
r2 = []

for k in range(20):
    k = k+1
    KNN_model = KNeighborsRegressor(n_neighbors=k).fit(x_train, y_train)
    y_fit_k = KNN_model.predict(x_test)
    mse.append(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_fit_k))
    r2.append(r2_score(y_test, y_fit_k))
    
mse_df = pd.DataFrame(mse)
mse_df.plot()
